  <title translate="true">Round</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword translate="true">Round</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para style="margin-bottom:10px; line-height:2.0;"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Round</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Round</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">(Value) converts Value to the nearest integer. &#160;In the case of a number that is exactly halfway between two integers, it converts it to whichever one is even.  If the number being rounded is outside the range -(2</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:8pt; vertical-align:super;" translate="true">31</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">-1) and +(2</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:8pt; vertical-align:super;" translate="true">31</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">-1), the function will return whichever of those numbers is closest. </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">See also </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Trunc" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Trunc</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">.</text></para>
  </body>
